! urxvt*background:rgba:1500/1800/2600/fa00
urxvt*background:rgba:1e00/2100/3700/fa00

! urxvt*background: #17273e
*.monitor1: eDP1
*.monitor2: DP2-2
*.monitor3: DP2-1
